This directory containts example scripts that are described in the book
"OpenGL Shading Language" by Randi J. Rost, Addison Wesley, and
available at the 3DLabs website
http://developer.3dlabs.com/openGL2/downloads/index.htm

The code is copyrighted by 3Dlabs and redistributable under the revised
BSD-license.  See 3Dlabs-License.txt in each example directories for
the details.

Each subdirectory contains a shell script run.sh to run the example
without installing Gauche-gl.
